subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Lorena Ochoa shot a four-over-par 76 — her highest score in nearly a year — in the MasterCard Classic in Huixquilucan, Mexico, leaving her nine strokes behind Jill McGill after the first round.Ochoa, who won by 11 strokes two weeks ago in Singapore, had six bogeys and two birdies on the hilly Bosque Real Country Club course. McGill, who is winless in 13 seasons on the Tour, shot a 67.
